title: 2010.03.14-F1.01.Bahrain.Race.BBC1_UK [TDMK1]
description:
2010.03.14-F1.01.Bahrain.Race.BBC1_UK-TDMK1.m4v

Jake Humphrey introduces coverage of the Bahrain Grand Prix, the first race of 2010. Jenson Button, making his McLaren debut, will be eager to repeat the scorching start he made in 2009, when six wins put him on the way to the drivers' title. However, fellow Briton Lewis Hamilton will want to prove he is the man to beat. Seven-times world champion Michael Schumacher will line up for the Mercedes team.


Now encoded as 'MP4 All Play'... As a departure from the DivX files which I have uploaded in the past, I've made the decision to get with the 21st century & start encoding with the following specs this year;

MP4 - 640x352 - 800Kb/s H264 Video - 44.1KHz/128Kbps Stereo AAC Audio

My belief is this is the best all round setup, and hopefuly you will agree!

This video will play on a computer with VLC, XBMC, XBox360, PS3 & all iPhones - enjoy the show... :)
